def: To beat soundly; to thrash. [Obs. or Low] Beau. & Fl.
A kind of oven, or reverberatory furnace, used for thecalcination of sand and potash, and converting them into frit. Ure.
Pertaining to, producing, or expressing, sexual love; as,amatory potions.
Seven times ten; one more than sixty-nine.
One who, or that which, convinces; one who wins over by proof.
An alkaloid found with hyoscyamine (with which it is alsoisomeric) in henbane, and extracted as a white, amorphous, semisolidsubstance.
One who is versed in petrology.
